💭 🤔 🇺🇸 🇩🇪   The CIA knew about the plan to blow up Nord Stream and initially supported it, Der Spiegel reports, citing sources

 💬 According to the sources, the first meeting between CIA representatives and Ukrainian operatives took place in Kyiv’s Podil district in 2022, where the plans were presented to the Americans;
 💬 Follow-up talks were held afterward, during which the Ukrainians allegedly received signals that the CIA might even help with financing;
 💬 "They told our guys that it was good and would work," one source told the outlet. Later, Germany determined that the U.S. had changed its position and tried to dissuade the Ukrainians.

